title: Tesla Full Self Driving Is Now 'End-To-End AI'
description:
In this video I discuss the recent Tesla full self driving 'FSD' demo that Delon Musk livestreamed on Twitter 'X' showing a 45 minute drive around Palo Alto California, driving past Mark Zuckerbergs house and other places and the implications of FSD coming out of beta.
